      <p id="Par11">We first set a coordinate axis along the gap from left to right, and the left breakpoint of the gap is defined as the origin (Fig.Â <xref rid="Fig1" ref-type="fig">1</xref>b, c). Then we represent the genomic position of read <inline-formula id="IEq4"><alternatives><tex-math id="M33">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
