				\begin{document}$$\le c$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M238"><mml:mrow><mml:mo>â¤</mml:mo><mml:mi>c</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5367_Article_IEq89.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>), the weights for the observations are 1. When the residual exceeds the threshold <inline-formula id="IEq90"><alternatives><tex-math id="M239">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
