      <p id="Par14">A real example in âSectionÂ <xref rid="Sec12" ref-type="sec">RegCloserâs rationale of resolving the tandem repeat</xref>â will show that the above insert-size guided pairwise alignment indeed greatly reduces false overlaps.</p>
    </sec>
    <sec id="Sec6">
      <title>Representation of detected overlaps by linear regression model</title>
      <p id="Par15">In the coordinate axis along the gap, we aim to solve the true values of the readsâ genomic positions, <inline-formula id="IEq17"><alternatives><tex-math id="M59">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
