      <p id="Par38">In the robust regression stage, RegCloser detected and eliminated the influence of the remaining false overlaps. FigureÂ <xref rid="Fig3" ref-type="fig">3</xref>d shows the variation of the residual distribution along the process of the two-step robust regression. In Step 1, the IRLS algorithm started with the OLS estimate, and converged after 8 iterations. The proportion of zero residuals increased from <inline-formula id="IEq96"><alternatives><tex-math id="M265">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
